name: Sacha Dhawan
description:
Sacha Dhawan is a British actor of Indian descent. Currently on Hulu's 'The Great', and previously seen in Doctor Who and Marvel's Iron Fist. Also does some voicework, radio plays, and traditional theatre.

Trained for a little over 7.5k on SD1.5. Further attempts just led to his head looking like a fat peanut.
